{"tid":1390995,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】就警方施放催淚彈遭索償 盧偉聰暫不用出庭應訊","createTime":"2019-07-31T09:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T10:01:24.000Z","uid":165683,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"df4262ac9465c4c75c7edad345ef471eab4663c6","tid":1390995,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:52:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190731/59881976\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190731%2F59881976&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnZa0YVntLK4LebkCjpCDSOM%3D&h=58637f75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190731%2F59881976&h=ffba395f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190731/59881976</a><br />\n<br />\n6.12金鐘清場，警方向和平示威區發射催淚彈，險釀人踩人事故。科大博士生與另一名市民早前入稟小額錢債審裁處，各自向警務處處長盧偉聰索償7.5萬元，案件今早作簡短提訊。審裁官指出，兩人入稟控告盧偉聰，是針對其執行公務時的行為，因此根據《官方法律程序條例》，被告應為律政司司長。博士生一度指若由律政司委派代表出庭，或違反審裁處案件不可聘任律師代表的規定；惟審裁官指被告一方代表是以公職身份出庭，而非律師或大律師身分。案件押後至10月30日再訊。"},{"pid":"93aba9fc1b123c8fa999c44d912a4b4efbd23933","tid":1390995,"uid":12746,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGvrHtp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGvrHtp.png&h=cff3af3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3189e6d130a9a049387ebf9bbcb4f8e32b3d74e","tid":1390995,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港警察</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">知法犯法</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">污糟邋遢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">毫無人格</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">淪為垃圾</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">吞槍自殺</s